Falcon Test - Chat room
by Gergő Pásztor

INSTALL & UNINSTALL

See the 'INSTALL' file!


FEATURES

Chat room app:
- Different rooms
- Send messages with WebSocket
- Send messages with REST API
- Receiver messages with WebSocket
- See all archive messages with REST API
- See archive messages in one room with REST API

Technology stack:
- Language: Java 8
- Build system: Gradle
- Framework: Spring Boot with MVC, Spring Data, Spring Integration, Spring Cloud Stream, Spring Cloud Service Discovery
- Messaging: Kafka
- Database: Postgresql 9.4 with Hibernate (JPA)
- Service discovery: Zookeeper
- OS: Ubuntu (Docker image)
- Running environment: Docker and Docker Composer

